{"tid":312804,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人日日都會發夢？","createTime":"2017-07-07T18:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T19:34:32.000Z","uid":55456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b12a512f9ac17b2da0baca0fb6953625ef28525b","tid":312804,"uid":55456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:27:42.000Z","msg":"每逢放假休息就發夢 而家長假就日日發<br />\n有無人知咩事？ <br />\n雖然我都幾享受發夢個陣時 感覺上日日都有故仔睇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41a68cd51ccb021ece16d71da9465391a180641","tid":312804,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:38:46.000Z","msg":"第一 訓太多<br />\n第二 訓得差"},{"pid":"b3c48c787c7086ce6d5a38cb4ef16163708fade2","tid":312804,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:41:45.000Z","msg":"成日發<br />\n攰得制的話搭車訓都會發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e6662ea0c53644d6f46e326ee1460eb7656945","tid":312804,"uid":79906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日發<br />\n攰得制的話搭車訓都會發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我琴日搭車發夢<br />\n係隧道出口醒左跟住訓翻<br />\n醒又係隧道口<br />\n重重覆覆4次先真係醒左仲係隧道中間"},{"pid":"7b37ff895dca74186524bf110297ef6bc55f8d8e","tid":312804,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:56:48.000Z","msg":"基本上訓教就係會發夢<br />\n只係有時起身唔記得咁解"},{"pid":"40f93febf6d7ddbddd37743e85e7028f5074389b","tid":312804,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:59:04.000Z","msg":"琴晚發左好多夢<br />\n其中一個係比玻璃樽掉碎個窗<br />\n然後嚇到醒左<br />\n去睇周公解夢<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/025902_74c879dbde766c6878354dd6e7364a31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F025902_74c879dbde766c6878354dd6e7364a31.jpg&h=ec42baa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5438a61c3e9b73aa7e5d05cd66cea2b1830d47f6","tid":312804,"uid":94871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:01:44.000Z","msg":"日日都發 <br />\n至少記到一個夢<br />\n放假都算好d 但係 第2朝要番學番工既話 一定記得好多個<br />\n成日都試過發左5-6個夢 記到4-5個 起身果下好似冇訓過咁<br />\n好撚慘"},{"pid":"b4b5d8eb24197699d5f32231412c8895f30d704b","tid":312804,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:23:07.000Z","msg":"呢個星期日日發 發完都會記得"},{"pid":"993862cc25a54b5dcbb10f82cccbe1227ad2c043","tid":312804,"uid":39853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:24:59.000Z","msg":"經常夢見初戀女友，已經四年，擺脫唔到，一星期總有幾日發夢。"},{"pid":"4596ce14c4f7a9b39bf1b7b7972a738dcfa229e3","tid":312804,"uid":27112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:25:07.000Z","msg":"除非發發吓夢嚇醒，否則好少會記得自己發過夢。"},{"pid":"9eec7de57afd2e86e8744db000b2340cc3a4a3ed","tid":312804,"uid":124962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經常夢見初戀女友，已經四年，擺脫唔到，一星期總有幾日發夢。</blockquote><br />\n好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如試下唔好訓 可能見唔到佢"},{"pid":"f0b0b53b695f137b367948beb34905c9ba10e227","tid":312804,"uid":117346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:31:28.000Z","msg":"差唔多日日都發，都係得一兩個夢倒，有時記得少部份夢到咩，但多數都係無厘頭，唔知個夢想表達咩。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打同我一樣間唔中試過發預言夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea8fedfb8fca05c28982ff1f80104323e8f65f1","tid":312804,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:34:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差唔多日日都發，都係得一兩個夢倒，有時記得少部份夢到咩，但多數都係無厘頭，唔知個夢想表達咩。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打同我一樣間唔中試過發預言夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有⋯有時仲覺得好恐怖 去到啲夢中去過既地方 發生啲夢中見過既情節"}]}